This is a play project to have a ftp server/client. Not sure how long it would
take, hope it could be done soon. Here I will write done the design document
to track the whole system.


Client:

   Display
  +-----------------+
  |                 |
  |                 |
  +-----------------+             FTP Function
           ^                     +----------------------+
           |              +----> |                      |
           v             /       |                      |
   Command              /        +----------------------+
  +-----------------+  /
  |                 |             Network Connection         FTP Protocol
  |                 |            +----------------------+    +----------------+
  +-----------------+            |                      |    |                |
                                 |                      |    |                |
                                 +----------------------+    +----------------+

User Session:
  +----------------------------+
  | state                      |
  | remote host                |
  |                            |
  | current directory          |
  |                            |
  |                            |
  |                            |
  +----------------------------+

Server:

   User Info(access control)     Files
  +-----------------+           +------------------+
  |                 |           |                  |
  |                 |           |                  |
  |                 |           |                  |
  +-----------------+           +------------------+


   Connection Control            FTP Function
  +-----------------+           +----------------------+
  |                 |---------> |                      |
  |                 |           |                      |
  |                 |           +----------------------+
  +-----------------+                                                          
                                 Network Connection         FTP Protocol
                                +----------------------+    +----------------+
                                |                      |    |                |
                                |                      |    |                |
                                +----------------------+    +----------------+
